title: Alcatel 1 (16GB) 5.0" Full View Display, Removable Battery, FM Radio, Dual SIM GSM Unlocked US & Global 4G LTE International Version 5033E (Bluish Black)
description: The Alcatel 5033E is a 5.5-inch smartphone with a 720 x 1440 pixel resolution and an 18:9 ratio. It has 16 GB of storage and 1 GB of RAM. It is a 4G smartphone that uses the GSM cellular network and is unlocked. It has a 5 MP rear camera and a 2 MP front camera. It has a headphone jack and uses the Android operating system.
